remarks.summary: Still considerable restrictions in rail traffic after strike
remarks.text: Following a strike by the EVG trade union, there will still be restrictions from the end of the strike (approx. 11 a.m.) on Friday, 21 April until the end of the day. RE, RB and S-Bahn trains as well as long-distance trains may continue to be cancelled. Underground trains, trams, buses and ferries will continue to operate.
